Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10), golang-any
Standards-Version: 4.5.1
Homepage: https://github.com/MiguelRodo/repos

Package: repos
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, git
Description: Multi-repository management tool
 This package provides infrastructure for managing multiple related repositories
 as a unified workspace. It includes tools for:
  - Cloning and managing multiple Git repositories
  - Creating and managing Git worktrees
  - Generating VS Code workspace configurations
  - Running pipelines across repositories
 .
 Designed for any multi-repository workflow and project structure.
